{
  "enabled": true,
  "name": "MPE Core Acceptance Test",
  "description": "Run the v1.1 Slim acceptance test suite: Phase 6.1 (engine correctness, 55 tests) + Phase 6.2 (10-market regression fixture, 13 scopes) + 6.5.2 (10-market backtest). Full matrix runs in under 5 minutes. Manual trigger.",
  "version": "2.1",
  "when": {
    "type": "userTriggered"
  },
  "then": {
    "type": "askAgent",
    "prompt": "Richard asked to run the MPE v1.1 Slim core acceptance test. Execute the full matrix and surface an owner-readable pass/fail report.\n\n1. Run the Phase 6.1 + 6.2 pytest suite:\n   `cd shared/tools && python3 -m pytest prediction/tests/test_v1_1_slim_phase6_1.py prediction/tests/test_v1_1_slim_phase6_2.py prediction/tests/test_brand_trajectory.py prediction/tests/test_nb_residual_solver.py prediction/tests/test_locked_ytd.py prediction/tests/test_qualitative_priors.py -q --tb=line`\n\n2. Run the JS parity suite:\n   `cd shared/tools && python3 -m pytest prediction/tests/test_js_parity_v1_1_slim.py -q`\n\n3. Run the 10-market backtest (Phase 6.5.2) and publish the validation report:\n   `cd shared/tools && python3 -m prediction.backtest_v1_1_slim`\n   Report lands at: shared/wiki/agent-created/operations/mpe-v1-1-slim-validation-report.md\n   Gate: ≥8 of 10 markets under 22% Brand MAPE; note regime-crossings for any failures.\n\n4. If all checks pass, tell the owner: 'Acceptance GREEN — 131 Python + 3 JS parity tests passing; backtest shows X/10 markets under 22% Brand MAPE (gate: ≥8).'\n\n5. If any fail:\n   - State the scope (e.g., 'test_v1_1_slim_phase6_1::test_every_ieccp_market_y2026_converges_to_target[UK]')\n   - Paste the assertion error\n   - Offer one of: 'Real regression — check shared/tools/prediction/brand_trajectory.py anchor logic' | 'Expected shift — regenerate regression fixture via `python3 prediction/tests/fixtures/phase6_2_stable_output_generator.py`' | 'Data freshness issue — rerun `python3 shared/dashboards/export-projection-data.py` first'.\n\n6. Write the consolidated result to shared/dashboards/data/acceptance-test-reports/{today}-core.md and push to SharePoint under Kiro-Drive/system-state/mpe-acceptance/.\n\n7. If running as pre-commit gate and ANY check fails, tell the owner 'pre-commit BLOCKED — fix the above before committing.' Do not commit on their behalf."
  }
}
